{"surah":{"number":72,"name":"الجن","englishName":"Al-Jinn","englishTranslation":"The Jinn","ayahCount":28},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:32.831Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"Say, [O Muhammad], \"It has been revealed to me that a group of the jinn listened and said, 'Indeed, we have heard an amazing Qur'an.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","english":"Say","translit":"qul","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أُوحِىَ","english":"It has been revealed","translit":"ūḥiya","root":"وحي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَىَّ","english":"to me","translit":"ilayya","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَنَّهُ","english":"that","translit":"annahu","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱسْتَمَعَ","english":"listened","translit":"is'tamaʿa","root":"سمع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"نَفَرٌۭ","english":"a group","translit":"nafarun","root":"نفر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنِّ","english":"the jinn","translit":"l-jini","root":"جنن"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فَقَالُوٓا۟","english":"and they said","translit":"faqālū","root":"قول"},{"position":10,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"سَمِعْنَا","english":"heard","translit":"samiʿ'nā","root":"سمع"},{"position":12,"arabic":"قُرْءَانًا","english":"a Quran","translit":"qur'ānan","root":"قرأ"},{"position":13,"arabic":"عَجَبًۭا","english":"amazing","translit":"ʿajaban","root":"عجب"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"It guides to the right course, and we have believed in it. And we will never associate with our Lord anyone.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَهْدِىٓ","english":"It guides","translit":"yahdī","root":"هدي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلرُّشْدِ","english":"the right way","translit":"l-rush'di","root":"رشد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَـَٔامَنَّا","english":"so we believe","translit":"faāmannā","root":"أمن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِهِۦ ۖ","english":"in it","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَلَن","english":"and never","translit":"walan","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_002_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"نُّشْرِكَ","english":"we will associate","translit":"nush'rika","root":"شرك","audio":"wbw/072_002_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِرَبِّنَآ","english":"with our Lord","translit":"birabbinā","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/072_002_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَحَدًۭا","english":"anyone","translit":"aḥadan","root":"أحد","audio":"wbw/072_002_010.mp3"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And [it teaches] that exalted is the nobleness of our Lord; He has not taken a wife or a son","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ","english":"And that He","translit":"wa-annahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَعَـٰلَىٰ","english":"Exalted is","translit":"taʿālā","root":"علو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"جَدُّ","english":"(the) Majesty","translit":"jaddu","root":"جدد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّنَا","english":"(of) our Lord","translit":"rabbinā","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","english":"not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱتَّخَذَ","english":"He has taken","translit":"ittakhadha","root":"أخذ"},{"position":7,"arabic":"صَـٰحِبَةًۭ","english":"a wife","translit":"ṣāḥibatan","root":"صحب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَدًۭا","english":"a son","translit":"waladan","root":"ولد"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And that our foolish one has been saying about Allah an excessive transgression.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ","english":"And that he","translit":"wa-annahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"used to","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَقُولُ","english":"speak","translit":"yaqūlu","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَفِيهُنَا","english":"the foolish among us","translit":"safīhunā","root":"سفه"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"against","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":7,"arabic":"شَطَطًۭا","english":"an excessive transgression","translit":"shaṭaṭan","root":"شطط"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"And we had thought that mankind and the jinn would never speak about Allah a lie.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that we","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ظَنَنَّآ","english":"thought","translit":"ẓanannā","root":"ظنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَّن","english":"never","translit":"lan","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَقُولَ","english":"will say","translit":"taqūla","root":"قول"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسُ","english":"the men","translit":"l-insu","root":"أنس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱلْجِنُّ","english":"and the jinn","translit":"wal-jinu","root":"جنن"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"against","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":10,"arabic":"كَذِبًۭا","english":"any lie","translit":"kadhiban","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"And there were men from mankind who sought refuge in men from the jinn, so they [only] increased them in burden.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ","english":"And that","translit":"wa-annahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"(there) were","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رِجَالٌۭ","english":"men","translit":"rijālun","root":"رجل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"among","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسِ","english":"mankind","translit":"l-insi","root":"أنس"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَعُوذُونَ","english":"who sought refuge","translit":"yaʿūdhūna","root":"عوذ"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بِرِجَالٍۢ","english":"in (the) men","translit":"birijālin","root":"رجل"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنِّ","english":"the jinn","translit":"l-jini","root":"جنن"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَزَادُوهُمْ","english":"so they increased them","translit":"fazādūhum","root":"زيد"},{"position":11,"arabic":"رَهَقًۭا","english":"(in) burden","translit":"rahaqan","root":"رهق"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"And they had thought, as you thought, that Allah would never send anyone [as a messenger].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّهُمْ","english":"And that they","translit":"wa-annahum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ظَنُّوا۟","english":"thought","translit":"ẓannū","root":"ظنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَمَا","english":"as","translit":"kamā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ظَنَنتُمْ","english":"you thought","translit":"ẓanantum","root":"ظنن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَّن","english":"never","translit":"lan","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَبْعَثَ","english":"will raise","translit":"yabʿatha","root":"بعث"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَحَدًۭا","english":"anyone","translit":"aḥadan","root":"أحد"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"And we have sought [to reach] the heaven but found it filled with powerful guards and burning flames.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that we","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَمَسْنَا","english":"sought to touch","translit":"lamasnā","root":"لمس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءَ","english":"the heaven","translit":"l-samāa","root":"سمو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَوَجَدْنَـٰهَا","english":"but we found it","translit":"fawajadnāhā","root":"وجد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُلِئَتْ","english":"filled (with)","translit":"muli-at","root":"ملأ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"حَرَسًۭا","english":"guards","translit":"ḥarasan","root":"حرس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"شَدِيدًۭا","english":"severe","translit":"shadīdan","root":"شدد"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَشُهُبًۭا","english":"and flaming fires","translit":"washuhuban","root":"شهب"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And we used to sit therein in positions for hearing, but whoever listens now will find a burning flame lying in wait for him.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that we","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كُنَّا","english":"used to","translit":"kunnā","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَقْعُدُ","english":"sit","translit":"naqʿudu","root":"قعد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْهَا","english":"there in","translit":"min'hā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَقَـٰعِدَ","english":"positions","translit":"maqāʿida","root":"قعد"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لِلسَّمْعِ ۖ","english":"for hearing","translit":"lilssamʿi","root":"سمع"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَمَن","english":"but (he) who","translit":"faman","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_009_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَسْتَمِعِ","english":"listens","translit":"yastamiʿi","root":"سمع","audio":"wbw/072_009_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔانَ","english":"now","translit":"l-āna","root":"أون","audio":"wbw/072_009_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"يَجِدْ","english":"will find","translit":"yajid","root":"وجد","audio":"wbw/072_009_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_009_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"شِهَابًۭا","english":"a flaming fire","translit":"shihāban","root":"شهب","audio":"wbw/072_009_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"رَّصَدًۭا","english":"waiting","translit":"raṣadan","root":"رصد","audio":"wbw/072_009_014.mp3"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And we do not know [therefore] whether evil is intended for those on earth or whether their Lord intends for them a right course.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that we","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَدْرِىٓ","english":"we know","translit":"nadrī","root":"دري"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَشَرٌّ","english":"whether evil","translit":"asharrun","root":"شرر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أُرِيدَ","english":"is intended","translit":"urīda","root":"رود"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِمَن","english":"for (those) who","translit":"biman","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(are) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَرَادَ","english":"intends","translit":"arāda","root":"رود"},{"position":11,"arabic":"بِهِمْ","english":"for them","translit":"bihim","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"رَبُّهُمْ","english":"their Lord","translit":"rabbuhum","root":"ربب"},{"position":13,"arabic":"رَشَدًۭا","english":"a right path","translit":"rashadan","root":"رشد"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"And among us are the righteous, and among us are [others] not so; we were [of] divided ways.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that [we]","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنَّا","english":"among us","translit":"minnā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحُونَ","english":"(are) the righteous","translit":"l-ṣāliḥūna","root":"صلح"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَمِنَّا","english":"and among us","translit":"waminnā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"دُونَ","english":"(are) other than","translit":"dūna","root":"دون"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ ۖ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"كُنَّا","english":"We","translit":"kunnā","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/072_011_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"طَرَآئِقَ","english":"(are on) ways","translit":"ṭarāiqa","root":"طرق","audio":"wbw/072_011_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"قِدَدًۭا","english":"different","translit":"qidadan","root":"قدد","audio":"wbw/072_011_010.mp3"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And we have become certain that we will never cause failure to Allah upon earth, nor can we escape Him by flight.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that we","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ظَنَنَّآ","english":"[we] have become certain","translit":"ẓanannā","root":"ظنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَّن","english":"never","translit":"lan","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"نُّعْجِزَ","english":"we will cause failure","translit":"nuʿ'jiza","root":"عجز"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"(to) Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَن","english":"and never","translit":"walan","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"نُّعْجِزَهُۥ","english":"we can escape Him","translit":"nuʿ'jizahu","root":"عجز"},{"position":11,"arabic":"هَرَبًۭا","english":"(by) flight","translit":"haraban","root":"هرب"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"And when we heard the guidance, we believed in it. And whoever believes in his Lord will not fear deprivation or burden.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that [we]","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَمَّا","english":"when","translit":"lammā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"سَمِعْنَا","english":"we heard","translit":"samiʿ'nā","root":"سمع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْهُدَىٰٓ","english":"the Guidance","translit":"l-hudā","root":"هدي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ءَامَنَّا","english":"we believed","translit":"āmannā","root":"أمن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِهِۦ ۖ","english":"in it","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"faman","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_013_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنۢ","english":"believes","translit":"yu'min","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/072_013_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"بِرَبِّهِۦ","english":"in his Lord","translit":"birabbihi","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/072_013_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَلَا","english":"then not","translit":"falā","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_013_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"يَخَافُ","english":"he will fear","translit":"yakhāfu","root":"خوف","audio":"wbw/072_013_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"بَخْسًۭا","english":"any loss","translit":"bakhsan","root":"بخس","audio":"wbw/072_013_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_013_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"رَهَقًۭا","english":"any burden","translit":"rahaqan","root":"رهق","audio":"wbw/072_013_015.mp3"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And among us are Muslims [in submission to Allah], and among us are the unjust. And whoever has become Muslim - those have sought out the right course.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّا","english":"And that we","translit":"wa-annā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنَّا","english":"among us","translit":"minnā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُسْلِمُونَ","english":"(are) Muslims","translit":"l-mus'limūna","root":"سلم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَمِنَّا","english":"and among us","translit":"waminnā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْقَـٰسِطُونَ ۖ","english":"(are) unjust","translit":"l-qāsiṭūna","root":"قسط"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَمَنْ","english":"And whoever","translit":"faman","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_014_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَسْلَمَ","english":"submits","translit":"aslama","root":"سلم","audio":"wbw/072_014_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","english":"then those","translit":"fa-ulāika","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_014_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"تَحَرَّوْا۟","english":"have sought","translit":"taḥarraw","root":"حري","audio":"wbw/072_014_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"رَشَدًۭا","english":"(the) right path","translit":"rashadan","root":"رشد","audio":"wbw/072_014_011.mp3"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"But as for the unjust, they will be, for Hell, firewood.'","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا","english":"And as for","translit":"wa-ammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْقَـٰسِطُونَ","english":"the unjust","translit":"l-qāsiṭūna","root":"قسط"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَكَانُوا۟","english":"they will be","translit":"fakānū","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لِجَهَنَّمَ","english":"for Hell","translit":"lijahannama","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"حَطَبًۭا","english":"firewood","translit":"ḥaṭaban","root":"حطب"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"And [Allah revealed] that if they had remained straight on the way, We would have given them abundant provision","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَلَّوِ","english":"And that if","translit":"wa-allawi","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱسْتَقَـٰمُوا۟","english":"they had remained","translit":"is'taqāmū","root":"قوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلطَّرِيقَةِ","english":"the Way","translit":"l-ṭarīqati","root":"طرق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَأَسْقَيْنَـٰهُم","english":"surely We (would) have given them to drink","translit":"la-asqaynāhum","root":"سقي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَّآءً","english":"water","translit":"māan","root":"موه"},{"position":7,"arabic":"غَدَقًۭا","english":"(in) abundance","translit":"ghadaqan","root":"غدق"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"So We might test them therein. And whoever turns away from the remembrance of his Lord He will put into arduous punishment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِّنَفْتِنَهُمْ","english":"That We might test them","translit":"linaftinahum","root":"فتن"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهِ ۚ","english":"therein","translit":"fīhi","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_017_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُعْرِضْ","english":"turns away","translit":"yuʿ'riḍ","root":"عرض","audio":"wbw/072_017_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَن","english":"from","translit":"ʿan","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_017_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ذِكْرِ","english":"the Remembrance","translit":"dhik'ri","root":"ذكر","audio":"wbw/072_017_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"رَبِّهِۦ","english":"(of) his Lord","translit":"rabbihi","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/072_017_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَسْلُكْهُ","english":"He will make him enter","translit":"yasluk'hu","root":"سلك","audio":"wbw/072_017_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"عَذَابًۭا","english":"a punishment","translit":"ʿadhāban","root":"عذب","audio":"wbw/072_017_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"صَعَدًۭا","english":"severe","translit":"ṣaʿadan","root":"صعد","audio":"wbw/072_017_011.mp3"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"And [He revealed] that the masjids are for Allah, so do not invoke with Allah anyone.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّ","english":"And that","translit":"wa-anna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَسَـٰجِدَ","english":"the masjids","translit":"l-masājida","root":"سجد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ","english":"(are) for Allah","translit":"lillahi","root":"أله"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَلَا","english":"so (do) not","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَدْعُوا۟","english":"call","translit":"tadʿū","root":"دعو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَعَ","english":"with","translit":"maʿa","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَحَدًۭا","english":"anyone","translit":"aḥadan","root":"أحد"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"And that when the Servant of Allah stood up supplicating Him, they almost became about him a compacted mass.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ","english":"And that","translit":"wa-annahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَمَّا","english":"when","translit":"lammā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَامَ","english":"stood up","translit":"qāma","root":"قوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَبْدُ","english":"(the) slave","translit":"ʿabdu","root":"عبد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَدْعُوهُ","english":"calling (upon) Him","translit":"yadʿūhu","root":"دعو"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَادُوا۟","english":"they almost","translit":"kādū","root":"كود"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَكُونُونَ","english":"became","translit":"yakūnūna","root":"كون"},{"position":9,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"around him","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"لِبَدًۭا","english":"a compacted mass","translit":"libadan","root":"لبد"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"Say, [O Muhammad], \"I only invoke my Lord and do not associate with Him anyone.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","english":"Say","translit":"qul","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ","english":"Only","translit":"innamā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَدْعُوا۟","english":"I call upon","translit":"adʿū","root":"دعو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّى","english":"my Lord","translit":"rabbī","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَلَآ","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"أُشْرِكُ","english":"I associate","translit":"ush'riku","root":"شرك"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِۦٓ","english":"with Him","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَحَدًۭا","english":"anyone","translit":"aḥadan","root":"أحد"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"Say, \"Indeed, I do not possess for you [the power of] harm or right direction.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","english":"Say","translit":"qul","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنِّى","english":"Indeed, I","translit":"innī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَآ","english":"(do) not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَمْلِكُ","english":"possess","translit":"amliku","root":"ملك"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ضَرًّۭا","english":"any harm","translit":"ḍarran","root":"ضرر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"رَشَدًۭا","english":"right path","translit":"rashadan","root":"رشد"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"Say, \"Indeed, there will never protect me from Allah anyone [if I should disobey], nor will I find in other than Him a refuge.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","english":"Say","translit":"qul","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنِّى","english":"Indeed I","translit":"innī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَن","english":"never","translit":"lan","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُجِيرَنِى","english":"can protect me","translit":"yujīranī","root":"جور"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَحَدٌۭ","english":"anyone","translit":"aḥadun","root":"أحد"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَنْ","english":"and never","translit":"walan","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَجِدَ","english":"can I find","translit":"ajida","root":"وجد"},{"position":10,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"دُونِهِۦ","english":"besides Him","translit":"dūnihi","root":"دون"},{"position":12,"arabic":"مُلْتَحَدًا","english":"any refuge","translit":"mul'taḥadan","root":"لحد"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"But [I have for you] only notification from Allah, and His messages.\" And whoever disobeys Allah and His Messenger - then indeed, for him is the fire of Hell; they will abide therein forever.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"But","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَلَـٰغًۭا","english":"(the) notification","translit":"balāghan","root":"بلغ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَرِسَـٰلَـٰتِهِۦ ۚ","english":"and His Messages","translit":"warisālātihi","root":"رسل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_023_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَعْصِ","english":"disobeys","translit":"yaʿṣi","root":"عصي","audio":"wbw/072_023_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/072_023_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَرَسُولَهُۥ","english":"and His Messenger","translit":"warasūlahu","root":"رسل","audio":"wbw/072_023_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","english":"then indeed","translit":"fa-inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_023_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_023_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"نَارَ","english":"(is the) Fire","translit":"nāra","root":"نور","audio":"wbw/072_023_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","english":"(of) Hell","translit":"jahannama","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_023_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"خَـٰلِدِينَ","english":"(they will) abide","translit":"khālidīna","root":"خلد","audio":"wbw/072_023_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"فِيهَآ","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/072_023_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"أَبَدًا","english":"forever","translit":"abadan","root":"أبد","audio":"wbw/072_023_017.mp3"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"[The disbelievers continue] until, when they see that which they are promised, then they will know who is weaker in helpers and less in number.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ","english":"Until","translit":"ḥattā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"when","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَأَوْا۟","english":"they see","translit":"ra-aw","root":"رأي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يُوعَدُونَ","english":"they are promised","translit":"yūʿadūna","root":"وعد"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَسَيَعْلَمُونَ","english":"then they will know","translit":"fasayaʿlamūna","root":"علم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَضْعَفُ","english":"(is) weaker","translit":"aḍʿafu","root":"ضعف"},{"position":9,"arabic":"نَاصِرًۭا","english":"(in) helpers","translit":"nāṣiran","root":"نصر"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَأَقَلُّ","english":"and fewer","translit":"wa-aqallu","root":"قلل"},{"position":11,"arabic":"عَدَدًۭا","english":"(in) number","translit":"ʿadadan","root":"عدد"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"Say, \"I do not know if what you are promised is near or if my Lord will grant for it a [long] period.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","english":"Say","translit":"qul","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِنْ","english":"Not","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَدْرِىٓ","english":"I know","translit":"adrī","root":"دري"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَقَرِيبٌۭ","english":"whether is near","translit":"aqarībun","root":"قرب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"تُوعَدُونَ","english":"you are promised","translit":"tūʿadūna","root":"وعد"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"or (whether)","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَجْعَلُ","english":"will appoint","translit":"yajʿalu","root":"جعل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"for it","translit":"lahu","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"رَبِّىٓ","english":"my Lord","translit":"rabbī","root":"ربب"},{"position":11,"arabic":"أَمَدًا","english":"a (distant) term","translit":"amadan","root":"أمد"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"[He is] Knower of the unseen, and He does not disclose His [knowledge of the] unseen to anyone","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَـٰلِمُ","english":"(The) All-Knower","translit":"ʿālimu","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْبِ","english":"(of) the unseen","translit":"l-ghaybi","root":"غيب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَلَا","english":"so not","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُظْهِرُ","english":"He reveals","translit":"yuẓ'hiru","root":"ظهر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"from","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"غَيْبِهِۦٓ","english":"His unseen","translit":"ghaybihi","root":"غيب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"أَحَدًا","english":"(to) anyone","translit":"aḥadan","root":"أحد"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"Except whom He has approved of messengers, and indeed, He sends before each messenger and behind him observers","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"Except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَنِ","english":"whom","translit":"mani","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱرْتَضَىٰ","english":"He has approved","translit":"ir'taḍā","root":"رضو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَّسُولٍۢ","english":"a Messenger","translit":"rasūlin","root":"رسل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَإِنَّهُۥ","english":"and indeed, He","translit":"fa-innahu","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَسْلُكُ","english":"makes to march","translit":"yasluku","root":"سلك"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِنۢ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"بَيْنِ","english":"before","translit":"bayni","root":"بين"},{"position":10,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ","english":"him","translit":"yadayhi","root":"يدي"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَمِنْ","english":"and from","translit":"wamin","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"خَلْفِهِۦ","english":"behind him","translit":"khalfihi","root":"خلف"},{"position":13,"arabic":"رَصَدًۭا","english":"a guard","translit":"raṣadan","root":"رصد"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"That he may know that they have conveyed the messages of their Lord; and He has encompassed whatever is with them and has enumerated all things in number.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِّيَعْلَمَ","english":"That He may make evident","translit":"liyaʿlama","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"indeed","translit":"qad","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَبْلَغُوا۟","english":"they have conveyed","translit":"ablaghū","root":"بلغ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"رِسَـٰلَـٰتِ","english":"(the) Messages","translit":"risālāti","root":"رسل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","english":"(of) their Lord","translit":"rabbihim","root":"ربب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَأَحَاطَ","english":"and He has encompassed","translit":"wa-aḥāṭa","root":"حوط"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"what","translit":"bimā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَدَيْهِمْ","english":"(is) with them","translit":"ladayhim","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَأَحْصَىٰ","english":"and He takes account","translit":"wa-aḥṣā","root":"حصي"},{"position":11,"arabic":"كُلَّ","english":"(of) all","translit":"kulla","root":"كلل"},{"position":12,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","english":"things","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":13,"arabic":"عَدَدًۢا","english":"(in) number","translit":"ʿadadan","root":"عدد"}]}]}
